Package: ssh-alertd
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Amekiri Studio <noreply@amekiri.studio>
Depends: systemd
Recommends: openssh-server
Homepage: https://github.com/Amekiri-Studio/ssh-alertd
Description: SSH login alert daemon
 Watches sshd logs and sends an alert on every successful SSH login.
 Telegram is supported today; WeCom, DingTalk, Feishu, WhatsApp and SMTP
 backends are planned. Each alert includes the client IP, username,
 client source port, authentication method and time.
